Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:39.26,ENG OP 2,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\blur10}The number of people that I can only speak to in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:40.93,ENG OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\be1}keep increasing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:40.93,ENG OP 2,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\blur10}keep increasing
